&lt;h1 class="relative group">॥ छान्दोग्योपनिषत् ॥
&lt;div id="-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
