class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 1
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-1" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-1" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>॥ अथ छान्दोग्योपनिषत् ॥ &lt;br>
ॐ आप्यायन्तु ममाङ्गानि वाक्प्राणश्च्क्षुः श्रोत्रमथो बलमिन्द्रियाणि च सर्वाणि । &lt;br>
सर्वं ब्रह्मौपनिषदं माहं ब्रह्म निराकुर्यां मा मा ब्रह्म निराकरोदनिकारणमस्त्वनिकारणं मेऽस्तु । &lt;br>
तदात्मनि निरते य उपनिषत्सु धर्मास्ते मयि सन्तु ते मयि सन्तु ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>॥ ॐ शान्तिः शान्तिः शान्तिः ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 2 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् द्वितीयोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-2/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-2/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् द्वितीयोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 2
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-2" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-2" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>समस्तस्य खलु साम्न उपासनꣳ साधु यत्खलु साधु &lt;br>
तत्सामेत्याचक्षते यदसाधु तदसामेति ॥ २.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>तदुताप्याहुः साम्नैनमुपागादिति साधुनैनमुपागादित्येव &lt;br>
तदाहुरसाम्नैनमुपागादित्यसाधुनैनमुपगादित्येव &lt;br>
तदाहुः ॥ २.१.२॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>अथोताप्याहुः साम नो बतेति यत्साधु भवति साधु बतेत्येव &lt;br>
तदाहुरसाम नो बतेति यदसाधु भवत्यसाधु बतेत्येव &lt;br>
तदाहुः ॥ २.१.३॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 3 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् तृतीयोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-3/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-3/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् तृतीयोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 3
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-3" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-3" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>असौ वा आदित्यो देवमधु तस्य द्यौरेव &lt;br>
तिरश्चीनवꣳशोऽन्तरिक्षमपूपो मरीचयः पुत्राः ॥ ३.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>तस्य ये प्राञ्चो रश्मयस्ता एवास्य प्राच्यो मधुनाड्यः । &lt;br>
ऋच एव मधुकृत ऋग्वेद एव पुष्पं ता अमृता &lt;br>
आपस्ता वा एता ऋचः ॥ ३.१.२॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>एतमृग्वेदमभ्यतपꣳस्तस्याभितप्तस्य यशस्तेज &lt;br>
इन्द्रियं वीर्यमन्नाद्यꣳरसोऽजायत ॥ ३.१.३॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 4 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् चतुर्थोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-4/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् चतुर्थोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 4
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-4" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-4" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>जानश्रुतिर्ह पौत्रायणः श्रद्धादेयो बहुदायी बहुपाक्य आस &lt;br>
स ह सर्वत आवसथान्मापयांचक्रे सर्वत एव &lt;br>
मेऽन्नमत्स्यन्तीति ॥ ४.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>अथ हꣳसा निशायामतिपेतुस्तद्धैवꣳ हꣳ सोहꣳ समभ्युवाद &lt;br>
हो होऽयि भल्लाक्ष भल्लाक्ष जानश्रुतेः पौत्रायणस्य &lt;br>
समं दिवा ज्योतिराततं तन्मा प्रसाङ्क्षी स्तत्त्वा &lt;br>
मा प्रधाक्षीरिति ॥ ४.१.२॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 5 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् पञ्चमोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-5/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् पञ्चमोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 5
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-5" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-5" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>यो ह वै ज्येष्ठं च श्रेष्ठं च वेद ज्येष्ठश्च ह वै श्रेष्ठश्च &lt;br>
भवति प्राणो वाव ज्येष्ठश्च श्रेष्ठश्च ॥ ५.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>यो ह वै वसिष्ठं वेद वसिष्ठो ह स्वानां भवति वाग्वाव वसिष्ठः ॥ ५.१.२॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>यो ह वै प्रतिष्ठां वेद प्रति ह तिष्ठत्यस्मिꣳश्च &lt;br>
लोकेऽमुष्मिꣳश्च चक्षुर्वाव प्रतिष्ठा ॥ ५.१.३॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 6 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् षष्ठोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-6/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-6/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् षष्ठोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A0%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A0%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 6
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-6" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-6" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>श्वेतकेतुर्हारुणेय आस तꣳ ह पितोवाच श्वेतकेतो &lt;br>
वस ब्रह्मचर्यं न वै सोम्यास्मत्कुलीनोऽननूच्य &lt;br>
ब्रह्मबन्धुरिव भवतीति ॥ ६.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>स ह द्वादशवर्ष उपेत्य चतुर्विꣳशतिवर्षः &lt;br>
सर्वान्वेदानधीत्य महामना अनूचानमानी स्तब्ध &lt;br>
एयाय तꣳह पितोवाच ॥ ६.१.२॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>श्वेतकेतो यन्नु सोम्येदं महामना अनूचानमानी &lt;br>
स्तब्धोऽस्युत तमादेशमप्राक्ष्यः येनाश्रुतꣳ श्रुतं &lt;br>
भवत्यमतं मतमविज्ञातं विज्ञातमिति कथं नु भगवः &lt;br>
स आदेशो भवतीति ॥ ६.१.३॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 7 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् सप्तमोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-7/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-7/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Upanishad.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">छान्दोग्योपनिषत् सप्तमोऽध्यायः
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Chandogyopnishad 7
&lt;div id="chandogyopnishad-7" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#chandogyopnishad-7" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>अधीहि भगव इति होपससाद सनत्कुमारं नारदस्तꣳ &lt;br>
होवाच यद्वेत्थ तेन मोपसीद ततस्त ऊर्ध्वं वक्ष्यामीति स होवाच ॥ ७.१.१॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>ऋग्वेदं भगवोऽध्येमि यजुर्वेदꣳ सामवेदमाथर्वणं &lt;br>
चतुर्थमितिहासपुराणं पञ्चमं वेदानां वेदं पित्र्यꣳ राशिं &lt;br>
दैवं निधिं वाकोवाक्यमेकायनं देवविद्यां ब्रह्मविद्यां &lt;br>
भूतविद्यां क्षत्रविद्यां नक्षत्रविद्याꣳ &lt;br>
सर्पदेवजनविद्यामेतद्भगवोऽध्येमि ॥ ७.१.२॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Chandogyopnishad 8 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् अष्टमोऽध्यायः</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-8/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-8/</guid><description>&lt;p>
